name: Alexis Rodriguez
summary: Alexis Rodriguez, a 27-year-old woman who identifies as straight, currently resides in Los Angeles, California. Originally from Miami, Florida, she is a software engineer in the tech industry after completing her undergraduate studies at UCLA. She is a fluent speaker of English and Spanish and upholds the values of hard work, family, and education. Her interests are traveling, reading, and coding. Although Alexis identifies as an atheist and holds liberal political views, she is looking for a long-term, monogamous relationship. She does not currently have children, but is open to having them in the future. Alexis is a Gemini and ENFP personality type who occasionally enjoys a drink but does not smoke or use marijuana or drugs. She is physically active and has a pet dog. Her ideal partner would be a straight man, aged between 25 and 35, who leads a healthy lifestyle, does not use substances, and has the same outlook towards having children.
